  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/c6bcf2bf1fddfc1ab8bc84c2199ff773.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/c6bcf2bf1fddfc1ab8bc84c2199ff773.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/c6bcf2bf1fddfc1ab8bc84c2199ff773.mp4?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Eat, Shoot, Dive, Repeat</strong> <br>Monkey Splash!! is an arcade, action platformer featuring monkeys, diving, and historical landmarks from around the world! Fire your Juice Beam to propel your funky monkey up these colossal structures to get the best height for the ultimate dive. Be careful, as rival divers, a fitness-obsessed rabbit and an anarchist duck will aim to put an end to your odyssey of aqua aerobics! Only the cheekiest will make it to the top...<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Shoot to Ascend:</strong> Simple One-Click Control<br></li><li><strong>Water Pollution:</strong> Deadly Diver enemies block your path, it will be a perilous climb.<br></li><li><strong>1 of your 5-a-Day:</strong> A variety of Fruity Power Ups will add flavour to your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/f008d83c328bad45ef6f8ad295ddf53f.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/f008d83c328bad45ef6f8ad295ddf53f.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/f008d83c328bad45ef6f8ad295ddf53f.mp4?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Summer Soundtrack:</strong> A different sun soaked club beat for every world landmark.<br></li><li><strong>Simian Surprise:</strong> A zany cast of Monkeys will put a smile on your face!<br></li><li><strong>The Perfect 10:</strong> Find the hidden Postcards and compete for the best level Score! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/91eeb016692cfb052b8b50ed43a9a504.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/91eeb016692cfb052b8b50ed43a9a504.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/91eeb016692cfb052b8b50ed43a9a504.mp4?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Rabbit Races:</strong> Speedy Levels featuring the juiced up Jerome the Jacked Rabbit.<br></li><li><strong>Duck and Dodge:</strong> Brand new Boss Levels featuring showdowns with Scorch Duck.<br></li><li><strong>World Trivia:</strong> Learn a few facts from top-traveller Ned the Easter Island Head </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/868a0cd9ccfe9b581f673c647a27aebe.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/868a0cd9ccfe9b581f673c647a27aebe.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/868a0cd9ccfe9b581f673c647a27aebe.mp4?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/c6bcf2bf1fddfc1ab8bc84c2199ff773.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/c6bcf2bf1fddfc1ab8bc84c2199ff773.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/c6bcf2bf1fddfc1ab8bc84c2199ff773.mp4?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Eat, Shoot, Dive, Repeat</strong> <br>Monkey Splash!! is an arcade, action platformer featuring monkeys, diving, and historical landmarks from around the world! Fire your Juice Beam to propel your funky monkey up these colossal structures to get the best height for the ultimate dive. Be careful, as rival divers, a fitness-obsessed rabbit and an anarchist duck will aim to put an end to your odyssey of aqua aerobics! Only the cheekiest will make it to the top...<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Shoot to Ascend:</strong> Simple One-Click Control<br></li><li><strong>Water Pollution:</strong> Deadly Diver enemies block your path, it will be a perilous climb.<br></li><li><strong>1 of your 5-a-Day:</strong> A variety of Fruity Power Ups will add flavour to your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/f008d83c328bad45ef6f8ad295ddf53f.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/f008d83c328bad45ef6f8ad295ddf53f.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/f008d83c328bad45ef6f8ad2